## 2) Ma trận quyền → API

| API | Method | Role |
|-----|--------|------|
| `/admin/users` | GET | ADMIN |
| `/admin/users/:userId/lock` | PATCH body `{ "locked": boolean }` | ADMIN |
| `/admin/workspaces` | GET | ADMIN |
| `/admin/workspaces/:workspaceId/disable` | PATCH | ADMIN |
| `/admin/audit-logs` | GET query `workspaceId?`, `action?`, `limit?` | ADMIN |
| `/users` | GET | ADMIN |
| `/topups/webhook` | POST body mock webhook | ADMIN |
| `/admin/quick-chat/agents` | GET | ADMIN |
| `/admin/quick-chat/tools` | GET | ADMIN |
| `/admin/quick-chat/agents/:agentId` | PUT | ADMIN |
| `/internal/quick-chat/sessions` | POST | ADMIN, STAFF |
| `/internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId` | GET | ADMIN, STAFF |
| `/internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId/messages` | POST | ADMIN, STAFF |
| `/internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId/actions/:actionId/confirm` | POST | ADMIN, STAFF |
| `/internal/templates/:templateId/approve` | POST body `{ "providerTemplateId"?: string }` | **STAFF** |
| `/internal/templates/:templateId/reject` | POST body `{ "reason": string }` | **STAFF** |

Ghi chú:
- `GET /users` và `GET /admin/users` hiện trả dữ liệu user tương đương cho mục đích list; FE có thể chỉ dùng **`GET /admin/users`** cho trang `/admin/users` để gọn namespace.
- Duyệt template **không** nằm trong `/admin/*` API — staff dùng `/internal/templates/...`.

